The paper deals with a machine learning problem of incorporating multi-modality of data distribution into a Gaussian Process regression model. This problem is typically studied in the field of machine learning, specifically in sub-fields such as statistical learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), statistics (cs.ST), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
